T02D3663:267a-1: badzra shr'i kham le s'a dha nam /
T02D3663:267a-3: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sgrub thabs /
T02D3663:267a-4: bcom ldan 'das ma rdo rje lu gu rgyud la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3663:267a-5: sngar bstan pa'i cho gas snying gar zla ba'i dkyil
T02D3663:267a-6: 'khor la h'um gi yi ge ljang gu las grub
T02D3663:267a-7: pa'i rdo rje lu gu rgyud zhal gsum phyag drug
T02D3663:267a-8: ma / zhal g-yas pa dang cig shos sngo ba dang dkar ba /
T02D3663:267b-0: zhal so so la spyan gsum gsum @267b mnga' ba /
T02D3663:267b-1: phyag g-yas gsum na rdo rje dang lcags sgrog dang mda'/
T02D3663:267b-2: phyag g-yon gsum na sdigs mdzub dang zhags pa dang /
T02D3663:267b-4: sku mdog sngo bsangs su ljang ba /
T02D3663:267b-6: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa sems can sdang ba
T02D3663:267b-7: rnams 'joms par byed par bdag nyid bsgoms la phyag
T02D3663:267b-9: de la lag pa gnyis khu tshur so sor bcings
T02D3663:267b-10: la mthe'u chung dang mdzub mo lcags sgrog gi rnam
T02D3663:267b-13: aom badzra shr'i kham le h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02D3663:267b-15: 'di ni rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sgrub thabs /
T02D3663:267b-16: slob dpon chen po dzee ta ri dgar las rnam par rgyal bas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02D3663:267b-18: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po pandi ta su ma ti k'irti dang /
T02D3663:267b-19: bod kyi lo ts'a ba mkhas pa mar ba chos
